<HEAD><TITLE>Powers and Prospects</TITLE>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">

<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER><TR><TD> <A HREF="../index.html">Archive</A> | <A HREF="http://www.worldmedia.com/">New World Media</A> | <A HREF="http://www.lbbs.org/sep/sep.htm">South End Press</A></TD></TR></TABLE>

<P><FONT SIZE=5><I>Excerpts from</I></FONT><BR>
<FONT SIZE=7 FACE="Arial, Helvetica"><B><I>Powers and Prospects</B></I></FONT><BR>
<FONT SIZE=5>Reflections on Human Nature and the Social Order</FONT>
<P><FONT SIZE=6 FACE="Arial, Helvetica"><B><SAMP>Noam Chomsky</SAMP></B></FONT>

<P>Boston: <A HREF="http://www.lbbs.org/sep/sep.htm">South End Press</A>, 1996</FONT>

<P>Order <I>Powers and Prospects</I> and receive a 40 percent discount on an additional Chomsky title published by South End Press, or become a member of South End Press and receive two free paperbacks plus a 40 percent discount on all additional titles for one year. To order, call 1-800-533-8478. 

<A NAME="contents">
<P><TABLE BORDER=2 ALIGN=CENTER CELLPADDING=5>
<TR><TD WIDTH=33% VALIGN=TOP NOWRAP>

<H3>Contents</H3>

