<P><FONT SIZE=2><A NAME="FN2.10" HREF="#TXT2.10">10</A></FONT> <CITE>BW,</CITE> May 23, 1994; see my articles in <CITE>Lies of Our Times,</CITE> August 1994; <CITE>Index on Censorship,</CITE> July/August 1994. Scott Allen, <CITE>BG,</CITE> Dec. 19, 1994.

